_sText:
Hi! This is my new Saw map. After making this a long time, i finally got it here.

This map is kind of "room escape" map, so to find a way out you have to solve several puzzles. And thats why this map is a bit different than other saw maps.

Some rooms in this map are from the Saw movies, and i have tried to make them look realistic. Hope you like it!

Final fix done. I also added walktrough txt. file in the download, but its recommended use only if you really dont know what to do.

Check out my other maps too------->[here!](http://www.gamebanana.com/members/submissions/maps/907575 "")
